      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0648P0-03133'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_248' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0648P0-03134'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_249' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clauses 71 and 72 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0648P0-03135'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_250' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 5 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0648P0-03136'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_251' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clauses 73 to 76 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-03137'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_252'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-mcintosh' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_252' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew McIntosh' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-mcintosh" title="Mr Andrew McIntosh">Lord McIntosh of Haringey</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This may be a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn until Thursday 5th June at 3.45 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0648P0-03138'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030519_GCR_253' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at twenty-eight minutes before eight o'clock.
      </p>
